    "rich_text_n7LtAC": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "OUR ROOTS",
        "rich_text": "<p>Our story goes back to 1947, when our family first stepped into the world of textiles. What started as a simple fabric trading business has grown over the decades into something much bigger; a legacy of craftsmanship, quality, and innovation.</p><p>For generations, we’ve been at the heart of India’s textile industry, supplying some of the country’s biggest retail brands. But we knew we could take things further. With years of expertise under our belt and a deep passion for creating something meaningful, we set out to build a brand that truly speaks to the modern man.</p><p>This isn’t just about clothing; it’s about heritage, quality, and a commitment to excellence. Every garment we create is thoughtfully designed, blending timeless craftsmanship with contemporary style. Our goal? To make pieces that don’t just look good but feel good, last long, and tell a story.</p><p>From our family to yours, welcome to a brand built on tradition, shaped by experience, and crafted for today.</p>",
        "page": "",
        "link": "",
        "link_text": "",
        "background": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
        "color": "#173250",
        "width": 100,
        "align_text": "center",
        "section_padding": "none"
      }
    },
